{
  "id": 5120827674722304,
  "name": ":target-before and :target-after pseudo-classes",
  "summary": "These pseudo-classes match scroll markers that are, respectively, before or after the active marker (the one matching :target-current) within the same scroll marker group, as determined by flat tree order:\r\n\r\n* :target-before matches all scroll markers that precede the active marker in the flat tree order within the group.\r\n\r\n* :target-after matches all scroll markers that follow the active marker in the flat tree order within the group.\r\n\r\n",
